# Matrix-Client deployed  [https://git.heroku.com/matrix-rest.git](https://git.heroku.com/matrix-rest.git). 

Isomorphic app, implemented with React,Redux,Webpack, and server-side rendered with Express

To run localy you also need to run the REST-full API locally  [https://github.com/Dragomirc/Matrix-api](https://github.com/Dragomirc/Matrix-api)



1.`git clone https://github.com/Dragomirc/Matrix-client`

2.`npm i`

3. `npm run build`

4. `npm run start:watch`